# 🎯 Interactive Quiz Application

An interactive GUI Quiz Application developed using **Python** and **Tkinter**.

The application allows users to select different difficulty levels, answer multiple-choice questions, and receive their final score after completing the quiz.

---

## ✨ Features

✅ Beautiful Tkinter GUI

✅ Multiple Difficulty Levels
- Easy
- Medium
- Hard

✅ Randomized Questions

✅ JSON Question Database

✅ Countdown Timer

✅ Blinking Timer Warning

✅ Progress Bar

✅ Instant Answer Validation

✅ Final Score Display

✅ Restart Quiz

---

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- Python 3
- Tkinter
- JSON
- Random

