## ▶ How to Run

Clone repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/Interactive-Quiz-Application-Python.git
```

Install Python

Run

```bash
python main.py
```

---

## 🎮 Gameplay

1. Select Difficulty

2. Press Start Quiz

3. Answer each MCQ

4. Submit Answer

5. Timer keeps running

6. Final Score is displayed

